00:01:30.574 --> 00:01:31.990
It's not really a
laughing matter.

00:01:36.220 --> 00:01:38.630
So any questions from last time?

00:01:38.630 --> 00:01:42.710
Of course, the brainstem
reflexes we were talking about

00:01:42.710 --> 00:01:45.980
are also good for
other functions,

00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:50.300
like reducing the
effects of noise masking,

00:01:50.300 --> 00:01:55.410
allowing selective attention,
those types of functions.

00:01:55.410 --> 00:01:58.930
I also have experimental
